---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Eric Davidson-Sawyer, a web developer based in South Berwick, ME, helping local businesses build their online presence."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>A little bit about me and how I work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2>Hi, I'm Eric</h2>

          <p>
            I'm a software engineer based in South Berwick, Maine. After years of
            building software for companies large and small, I started helping local
            businesses with their web presence.
          </p>

          <p>
            I noticed that many local businesses either have outdated websites, no
            website at all, or are paying too much for basic services. I wanted to
            change that by offering straightforward, fairly-priced web development
            that actually serves the needs of small businesses.
          </p>

          <h3>My Approach</h3>

          <p>
            I believe in keeping things simple. You don't need a complicated website
            with dozens of features. You need a site that:
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>Looks professional and reflects your brand</li>
            <li>Loads fast (customers won't wait)</li>
            <li>Works perfectly on phones (that's where most people browse)</li>
            <li>Helps customers find you on Google</li>
            <li>Makes it easy to contact you or take the next step</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            That's what I focus on. No unnecessary complexity, no ongoing fees you
            don't understand, no jargon.
          </p>

          <h3>Why Local?</h3>

          <p>
            While I work with clients remotely too, there's something special about
            helping businesses in my own community. I shop at your stores, eat at
            your restaurants, and use your services. When you succeed, our whole
            community benefits.
          </p>

          <p>
            Plus, being local means I'm actually available. We can meet for coffee,
            I can stop by your shop, and I understand the local market you're
            serving.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="about-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-box">
            <h3>Technical Background</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>10+ years software engineering</li>
              <li>Full-stack development</li>
              <li>Modern web technologies</li>
              <li>Performance optimization</li>
              <li>SEO best practices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-box">
            <h3>Based In</h3>
            <p>South Berwick, ME</p>
            <p class="text-light">Serving the Seacoast region of Maine and New Hampshire</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Let's Work Together</h2>
      <p class="text-light">
        Ready to talk about your project? I'd love to hear what you're working on.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn mt-2">Get In Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-text h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .about-text li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--header-height) + 2rem);
  }

  .sidebar-box {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sidebar-box h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .sidebar-box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .sidebar-box li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .sidebar-box p {
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-sidebar {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .sidebar-box {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
